title: Kaspersky (Reset Trial)
description:
Everyone knows about Kaspersky so I will just skip the details. Many have been looking for ways to reset their trials to keep the service from interupting so i am giving back to the community.

Simply run the reset trial.exe file and there will be instructions on how to reset. It\&#039;s pretty self explanatory.

Btw, this is Kaspersky Internet Security 7.0.1.325 (latest at time of posting). If you do a custom install, you can choose which components NOT to install as the full installation I find to be a little performance degrading.

As with other people who share, be kind and seed for others to get.


Much Appreciated.
